John the sorcerer, a Simon the sorcerer clone

Install Pygame and Python (http://python.org http://pygame.org), then 
run 'python game.py' in this directory.

Walkto, Pickup and Talkto works, the rest is under development.

click on the buttons in the taskbar to do something.
as an example : push move, then click on the main screen and 
the player moves towards that position
